261
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,360
Nie, ja som...

262
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:14,210
Sada, prepáč...

263
00:17:14,210 --> 00:17:16,430
Um, s niekým si ma mýlite.

264
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:26,350
Som späť.

265
00:17:26,350 --> 00:17:27,060
Sada!

266
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:33,650
Čo sa deje starký?

267
00:17:33,650 --> 00:17:35,480
Bola si oživená.

268
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:39,120
Sada, vrátila si sa ku mne!

269
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:41,960
Neviem nič o tom, že by bola oživená,

270
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:45,290
