271
00:17:45,650 --> 00:17:48,290
Eh, to fakt?

272
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:51,530
Huh? Čo to práve robím?

273
00:17:51,530 --> 00:17:52,960
Dobrý bože.

274
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:58,320
Som zvedavá, či som bola odhalená.

275
00:18:01,890 --> 00:18:04,820
Otec asi teraz večeria.

276
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:08,990
A tu som ja v cudzom dome.

277
00:18:08,990 --> 00:18:12,190
A k tomu v chlapčenskej izbe.

278
00:18:19,150 --> 00:18:22,740
